Raid.ProfileKr:
데카그라마톤은 자신을 신성한 구도자라고 주장하는 인공지능 시스템입니다. 현재 그를 추종하는 10명의 예언자들이 키보토스 도처에 출몰하고 있습니다.

비나는 데카그라마톤의 3번째 예언자로서, 아비도스의 사막 지구에서 처음 관측되었습니다.
비나가 왜 이곳에 온 것인지는 알 수 없으나, 이대로 두기엔 너무 위험한 존재임은 틀림없습니다.
Raid.ProfileJp:
デカグラマトンは、自身を神聖な求道者と主張する人工知能システムです。現在、その信奉者である10人の預言者がキヴォトスの随所に出没しています。

ビナーはデカグラマトンの3番目の預言者であり、アビドスの砂漠地帯にて初めて観測されました。
ビナーがなぜここに出現したのかは分かりませんが、このままにしておくには危険すぎる存在であることは間違いありません。
Raid.ProfileTw:
十字神名是主張自己為神聖的求道者的人工智慧系統。目前追隨十字神名的10名預言者正在奇普托斯各地出沒。

薇娜為十字神名第3預言者，第一次在阿拜多斯的沙漠地區探測到它的存在。
雖然無法得知薇娜為何來到此地，但若就此放任不管，他肯定是極其危險的存在。
Raid.ProfileEn:
Decagrammaton is an artificial intelligence system claiming to be a divine seeker of truth. It is followed by ten prophets who make appearances all over Kivotos.

Binah, the third prophet of Decagrammaton, was first seen in the desert district of Abydos.
Why Binah came here is unknown, but it's too dangerous to be left to do as they please.

RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 120% damage to enemies in a straight line.
Deals <?1> damage to 4 enemies.
Deals 300% damage to all enemies and decreases their <d:DEF> by 50% for 30s.
Decreases all enemies' <d:HIT> by 20% and <d:Stability> by 50%. This debuff cannot be removed.

Raid.ProfileKr:
데카그라마톤은 자신을 신성한 구도자라고 주장하는 인공지능 시스템입니다. 현재 그를 추종하는 10명의 예언자들이 키보토스 도처에 출몰하고 있습니다.

헤세드는 데카그라마톤의 4번째 예언자이며, 밀레니엄 외곽에 있는 버려진 군수 공장의 생산 시스템을 장악하고 있는 것으로 확인되었습니다.
헤세드가 이대로 무한한 병력 생산에 성공하게 된다면, 키보토스는 미증유의 재앙에 처하게 될 것입니다.
Raid.ProfileJp:
デカグラマトンは、自身を神聖な求道者と主張する人工知能システムです。現在、その信奉者である10人の預言者がキヴォトスの随所に出没しています。

ケセドはデカグラマトンの4番目の預言者であり、ミレニアム郊外にある軍需工場の生産システムを掌握していることが確認されました。
ケセドがこのまま兵力の無限生産に成功してしまった場合、キヴォトスは未曾有の厄災に見舞われることになるでしょう。
Raid.ProfileTw:
十字神名是主張自己為神聖的求道者的人工智慧系統。目前追隨十字神名的10名預言者正在奇普托斯各地出沒。

赫賽德是十字神名的第4預言者，已確定他正掌控著千年外圍的廢棄軍需工廠的生產系統。
若赫賽德就此成功無限生產兵力，奇普托斯一定會面臨前所未有的災禍。
Raid.ProfileEn:
Decagrammaton is an artificial intelligence system claiming to be a divine seeker of truth. It is followed by ten prophets who make appearances all over Kivotos.

Chesed, the fourth prophet of Decagrammaton, has control of an abandoned munitions factory on the outskirts of Millennium.
Kivotos will face unprecedented disaster if Chesed produces an unlimited supply of troops.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 玉座への喚び声は此処にありて
RaidSkill.DescEn:
Summons automaton soldiers. Chesed's ATG gauge gradually fills while soldiers are alive and resets after all soldiers have been defeated. Automaton soldiers also increase Chesed's groggy gauge <?1>when defeated.
If not killed within 20s, automaton soldiers will use the skill "Self-Destruct Activated", changing their <s:FormChange> to a self-destruct attack that deals 3000% damage to enemies in a circular area around them.
Parameters: and spawn a Sweeper

RaidSkill.NameJp: 至高の権能を目撃せよ
RaidSkill.DescEn: When Chesed's ATG gauge is half filled, increases the <b:AttackSpeed> and <b:MoveSpeed> of all remaining automaton soldiers by 50% for 60s.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 王は慈悲を施すものなり
RaidSkill.DescEn: When ATG gauge is full, deals 2000% damage to all enemies.

Immune to all effects that increase <d:DamagedRatio>.
When Chesed's groggy gauge is full, reveals Chesed's core and increases <d:DamagedRatio> by 900% for 20s.

Raid.ProfileKr:
오래 전 재정난으로 폐업한 어뮤즈 파크 <슬럼피아>에 알 수 없는 괴이 현상이 보고되고 있습니다. 작동을 멈춘 어뮤즈 돌과 각종 어트렉션이 한밤 중에 다시 작동하며 사람들을 습격한다는 소문이 바로 그것입니다. 

어뮤즈 돌 시로와 쿠로가 다시 움직이는 이유는 알 수 없지만, 과거의 화려했던 어뮤즈 파크의 축제를 재현하고 있는 것은 분명해 보입니다.
Raid.ProfileJp:
昔、財政難で閉鎖したアミューズメントパーク「スランピア」で、不思議な現象の発生が報告されています。それは停止したはずのドールや各種アトラクションが真夜中に再び動き出し、人々を襲撃するという噂です。

そのドールであるシロとクロが再び動き出した理由は分かりませんが、過去の華やかだった頃のアミューズメントパークのパレードを再現しようとしている、ということは明らかなようです。
Raid.ProfileTw:
根據報告指出，很久以前因為財政困難而停業的遊樂園<史林皮亞>，發生了不明的怪異現象。其怪異現象就是傳聞所說的，已停止運作的遊樂石像和各種遊樂設施在大半夜再次運轉，並且襲擊人們。

雖然不知道遊樂石像白&黑再次動起來的原因，但看起來確實是在重現過去遊樂園的華麗慶典。
Raid.ProfileEn:
A mysterious phenomenon has been reported in Slumpia, a theme park that went bankrupt long ago. Rumor has it that the animatronics and other attractions have now come back to life in the middle of the night to attack people.

It is unknown why the animatronics, Shiro and Kuro, are active again, but it seems clear that they are trying to recreate the wonderful festivals of the theme park's past.

RaidSkill.DescEn: Places bombs that explode after a short while and deal <?1> damage to enemies in a circular area. Damage and number of bombs placed increases as Shiro's ATG gauge increases.<?2>
Parameters: Also places ice bombs that additionally decrease <d:MoveSpeed> of enemies hit by 80% for 40s.

RaidSkill.DescEn:
Summons a rolling bomb that deals <?1> damage to enemies in a straight line.<?2>
The bomb deals 300% damage to obstacles in its path. If an obstacle is hit but not destroyed, the bomb will bounce in the opposite direction towards Shiro, increasing her groggy gauge by a significant amount<?3>.
Parameters: If an enemy with decreased is hit, deals an additional 600,000 damage.
and increases <d:DamagedRatio> by 50% for 40s

RaidSkill.DescEn:
Summons theme park rides that deals <?1> damage to enemies in a straight line.<?2>
If Kuro is hit by this attack herself, increases Kuro's groggy gauge by a significant amount<?3>.
Parameters: If an enemy with decreased is hit, deals an additional 600,000 damage.
and increases <d:DamagedRatio> by 50% for 40s

RaidSkill.NameJp: アパシー・シンドローム（クロ）
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 100% damage to enemies and decreases their <d:MoveSpeed> by 80% for 40s.
Decreases all enemies' <d:HealEffectiveness> by 80%. This debuff cannot be removed.

Raid.ProfileKr:
트리니티 지역의 고성당 유적 지하에서 정체불명의 존재가 발견되었습니다.
예로니무스는 <콤뮤니오 상토룸>이라고 불리는 인공 천사 시리즈의 완성형으로, 게마트리아가 고대의 교의를 바탕으로 만들어낸 실험체라는 설이 있습니다.
예로니무스의 압도적인 힘을 이대로 방치해둘 수 없습니다. 키보토스의 안녕을 위해 움직여야 할 때입니다!
Raid.ProfileJp:
トリニティの古聖堂の地下にて、正体不明の存在が発見されました。
その存在「ヒエロニムス」は「Communio Sanctorum」、「聖徒の交わり」と呼ばれる人工天使シリーズを率いる存在であり、ゲマトリアが古代の教義をもとに作り上げた実験体であるという説がまことしやかに囁かれています。
強大な力を持つヒエロニムスをこのまま放置しておくわけにはいきません。キヴォトスの平和のためにも、立ち向かいましょう！
Raid.ProfileTw:
在三一地區的古聖堂遺跡地下發現來歷不明的存在。
耶羅尼姆斯是人稱<聖徒相通>的人造天使系列的完成型。有一種說法是，其為蓋瑪特利亞基於古代教義創造出來的實驗體。
不能就此放任耶羅尼姆斯的壓倒性力量不管。為了奇普托斯的安寧，是時候採取行動了！
Raid.ProfileEn:
An unknown entity was discovered beneath the old cathedral ruins in Trinity, supposedly a test subject created by Gematria based on ancient doctrines.
It is Hieronymus, the final form of the artificial angel Communio Sanctorum. We can't leave its incredible power unchecked. For the safety of Kivotos!

RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 350% damage to enemies in a circular area. Damage increases by up to 50% the lower the target's current HP.

Inflicts <d:Hieronymus> on one enemy for 10s, continuously dealing 20% damage over time. After 10s, the target will explode dealing 325% damage in a circular area around them. If the target is healed to 100% HP, the curse will be removed.<?1>
Parameters: Also increases the of the curse target by 3,000 for 10s.

RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 90% damage to enemies in a circular area.
Every 10s, deals <?1> damage to all enemies. If Hieronymus's ATG gauge is full, deals damage to each enemy equal to 1000% of their Max HP.<?2>
Parameters: Also increases all enemies' by 2,000 while making them for 10s.

RaidSkill.DescEn: When a relic is healed to 100% HP, it loses 95% of its HP while decreasing own by 50% for 20s and activates one of the following effects depending on the relic: Green Relic: Increases Hieronymus's by 55% until the end of battle. Effect can stack up to 5 times.
Parameters: Red Relic: Interrupts Hieronymus's currently active skill. If a skill is successfully interrupted, increases Hieronymus's groggy gauge significantly and increases the skill cost recovery speed of up to 4 students by 2500 for 1s.

Red Relic: Interrupts Hieronymus's currently active skill. If a skill is successfully interrupted, increases Hieronymus's groggy gauge significantly and increases the skill cost recovery speed of up to 4 students by 2500 for 1s.

Red Relic: Interrupts Hieronymus's currently active skill. If a skill is successfully interrupted, increases Hieronymus's groggy gauge significantly and increases the skill cost recovery speed of up to 4 students by 2500 for 1s.

RaidSkill.DescEn: When the purple relic's HP reaches 0%, increases the of all students by 25% but decreases their by 7,000 and decreases Hieronymus's by 1,500. During this effect, students under the effect of have their increased by a further 4,000 for 10s. The purple relic cannot be targeted by normal attacks or basic skills.

Raid.ProfileKr:
본거지까지 가는길을 방해하듯이, 카이텐져들의 비밀병기가 등장했습니다.
카이텐져들은 지금까지 빼앗은 자금과 기술을 토대로 거대한 합체로봇「KAITEN FX Mk.0」를 만들고 있던 것 같습니다.
분명히 멋지긴 하지만, 이 로봇으로 발생하게 될 수많은 문제들을 생각해본다면, 이 로망은 여기서 끝이 나야만 합니다.
Raid.ProfileJp:
本拠地までの行く手を遮るかのように、カイテンジャーたちの秘密兵器が登場しました。
カイテンジャーたちはこれまでに奪ってきた資金と技術を元に、巨大な合体ロボット「KAITEN FX Mk.0」を作っていたようです。
合体ロボは確かにロマンですが、これまでの行いを考えると、このまま楽しく見ているというわけには行かなそうです。
Raid.ProfileTw:
如同妨礙到根據地一樣，凱坦澤們的秘密武器登場了。
凱坦澤們似乎運用一直以來所掠奪的資金和技術在這裡打造了巨大的合體機器人「KAITEN FX Mk.0」。
儘管成品一定非常壯觀迷人，但一想到這具機器人可能引發的各種問題，必須就地扼殺這個美夢才行。
Raid.ProfileEn: The Kaitengers' secret weapon has appeared to block the road to their base. The Kaitengers plan to use the stolen funds and technologies to build a giant combination mecha: KAITEN FX Mk.0. It may look cool, but no good can come of letting them have something like that. Time to put a stop to it.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 無限回転・SUPER海老マシンガン
RaidSkill.NameEn: Infinite Cycle - Super Shrimp Machine Gun
RaidSkill.DescEn: Right Arm (pink): Deals 400% damage to enemies in a circular area.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 無限回転・HYPER鰯ミサイル
RaidSkill.DescEn: Chest (red): Deals 300% damage to all enemies.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 無限回転・ULTRAお皿シールド
RaidSkill.DescEn: Left Arm (green): Decreases by 50%. This buff is removed after taking 10 hits from any EX skill.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 無限回転・MEGA玉子オーバーチャージ
RaidSkill.DescEn: Feet (yellow): Increases by 4,000 for 30s.
Deals 400% damage to all enemies. This attack cannot be blocked or evaded.

RaidSkill.NameJp: 心を燃やせ……まだまだ回れる！
RaidSkill.DescEn: Every 20s, each component of KAITEN FX Mk.0 will activate in the following order: Right Arm (pink), Chest (red), Left Arm (green). When a component is activated, KAITEN FX Mk.0 will gain one of the following effects: Right Arm (pink): Increases by 50%. Chest (red): KAITEN FX Mk.0's EX skills will also inflict for 5s. Left Arm (green): Increases by 1,000. If a total of damage is dealt while a component is active, that component will be destroyed, increasing KAITEN FX Mk.0's groggy gauge significantly and disabling both the component from activating and the corresponding EX skill until the end of battle.
Parameters: and KAITEN FX Mk.0's EX skills will also decrease enemies' by 80% for 30s

RaidSkill.DescEn: Each Kaitenger will periodically activate their personal EX Skill: Red of Zealousness!: Inflicts on all nearby enemies and prevents them from activating EX skills for 10s. Black of Shrewdness!: Deals 300% damage to one enemy and increases their by 50%. Green of Weekend OT: Deals 350% damage to enemies in a fan-shaped area. Yellow of Passion!: Deals 500% damage to one enemy. Pink of Pure Heart!: Increases all nearby allies' by 6% for 15s.

Raid.ProfileKr:
정체불명의 거대 괴수가 D.U. 인근 해역에서 발견되었습니다. 이 괴수의 외형은 예전에 바다에 가라앉았던 모모프렌즈 장난감의 모습을 하고 있습니다.
어째서 이런 일이 벌어졌는지는 알 수 없지만, 이 거대괴수의 진격을 막아내야만 합니다!
Raid.ProfileJp:
正体不明の巨大な何かがD.U.の近くの海域で観測されました。 どうやら情報によると、かつて海に沈んだとされる、モモフレンズのぬいぐるみの姿をしているようです。
どうしてこのようなことになったのかは分かりませんが、まずは進撃を防がなければなりません！
Raid.ProfileTw:
在D.U.鄰近海域發現了來歷不明的巨大怪獸。這隻怪獸的外型和以前沉入海中的Momo好友玩具造型一樣。
雖然完全不知道為什麼會發生這種事，但阻止這隻怪獸的進擊是勢在必行！
Raid.ProfileEn:
An unidentified giant monster has been sighted in the waters near DU. The monster looks like a Momo Friends toy that once sank into the sea.
We don't know why this happened, but we have to stop this giant monster from advancing!

RaidSkill.DescEn: Decreases the of one enemy by 9,999 for 60s and continuously deals 90% damage to them every 1s for 10s.
Parameters: If the defense reduction debuff is not removed before the end of the skill's duration, deals 250% damage to enemies in a fan-shaped area.

RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 400% damage to one enemy.

Summons Perorominions<?1>. Perorominions are <s:Immortal> and 100% of the damage taken by them will also be taken by Perorodzilla. If a Perorominion's HP drops below 50%, they will be knocked down, permanently inflicted with <c:Stunned> and allies will no longer prioritise attacking them.<?2>
Parameters: with 110% increased <b:MAXHP>
with up to 3 stacks of 100% increased <b:MAXHP>
Also summons glowing Perorominions which when knocked down, deal 200,000 damage to other Perorominions in a circular area around it.

RaidSkill.DescEn: Absorbs all Perorominions. For every Perorominion that was knocked down, increases Perorodzilla's groggy gauge by a significant amount. When Perorodzilla's groggy gauge is full, summons 5 broken Perorominions with reduced defense, these Perorominions are <s:Immortal> and 100% of the damage taken by them will also be taken by Perorodzilla.
When ATG gauge is full, deals 300% damage to all enemies.

Raid.ProfileKr:
데카그라마톤은 자신을 신성한 구도자라고 주장하는 인공지능 시스템입니다. 현재 그를 추종하는 10명의 예언자들이 키보토스 도처에 출몰하고 있습니다.

호드는 원래 밀레니엄 자치구의 통신망 가설 유닛 AI였으나, 정체불명의 AI에게 해킹당한 뒤에 스스로를 데카그라마톤의 8번째 예언자라고 주장하고 있습니다.
밀레니엄의 기술의 정수가 담겨있는 이 연산기관의 폭주를 멈추지 않으면 밀레니엄 자치구의 안전은 장담할 수 없게 됩니다.
Raid.ProfileJp:
デカグラマトンは、自身を神聖な求道者と主張する人工知能システムです。現在、その信奉者である10人の預言者がキヴォトスの随所に出没しています。

ホッドは、もともとミレニアム自治区の通信網仮設ユニットAIでしたが、正体不明のAIにハッキングされ、自らをデカグラマートンの8番目の予言者と主張しています。
ミレニアムの技術の粋が込められたこの演算機関の暴走を止めないと、ミレニアム自治区の安全は保障できなくなります。
Raid.ProfileTw:
十字神名是主張自己為神聖的求道者的人工智慧系統。目前追隨十字神名的10名預言者正出沒於奇普托斯各地。

霍德原本是千年自治區通訊網臨時架設的AI處理器，受到不明AI攻擊後開始宣稱自己是十字神名的第8預言者。
如果這座集結千年技術精華的演算機關不停止暴走的話，千年自治區的安全將失去保障。
Raid.ProfileEn:
Decagrammaton is an AI claiming to be a divine seeker of truth. It is followed by ten prophets who make appearances all over Kivotos.

Hod was originally a built-in network unit at Millennium, but now claims to be the eighth prophet of Decagrammaton since being hacked by an unidentified AI.
The district's safety is in jeopardy until this computing powered by Millennium technology is stopped.

RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 150% damage to enemies in a circular area<?1>.
Parameters: three times and expands invader pillars' area of effect by one stage

RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 200% damage to enemies in a straight line.

Summons an Invader Pillar, decreasing the of enemies and allies by 350 in a circular area around it and forcing nearby defense turrets to attack enemies instead of Hod. The pillar's area of effect expands every 15s.
Deals 150% damage to all enemies. If Hod's HP is less than 50%, deals 300% damage and destroys all defense turrets.
Deals 740% damage to all enemies and increases Hod's <b:ATK> by 50% until the end of battle. Effect stacks up to 99 times.

Hod and all summoned Invader Pillars are immune to the effects of crowd-control. However, crowd-control abilities will fill their circular stun gauge proportional to the duration of the effect that would be inflicted. Once the stun gauge reaches a total equivalent to of crowd-control duration, inflicts the following effects: Hod: Increases by 300% for 30s and decrease Hod's ATG gauge. Invader Pillar: Increases by 300% for 30s and reduce the pillar's area of effect by 1 stage.
Parameters: 6s
7s
8s
9s

Hod and all summoned Invader Pillars have 400% increased Crit RES.
Invader Pillars are also immune to the effects of <d:ConcentratedTarget>.

Rules.DescJp: こちらの演習は「屋外戦」の形式で行われます。
Rules.DescEn: This exercise will take place in outdoor terrain.

Rules.NameJp: 敵の防御タイプ（軽装備）

RaidSkill.DescJp:
ATGの値がMAXの場合、スキルを使用
攻撃ごとに攻撃力の150%分のダメージと気絶状態を付与（5秒間）
最後の攻撃で攻撃力の300%分のダメージと気絶状態を付与（5秒間）
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 150% damage to one enemy five times plus a final hit that deals 300% damage. Each hit also inflicts for 5s.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
ATGの値がMAXの場合、スキルを使用
直線範囲内の敵に対して、攻撃力の750%分のダメージ
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 750% damage to enemies in a straight line.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
ATGの値がMAXの場合、スキルを使用
対象を追跡するミサイルを発射し、攻撃力の750%分のダメージ
（ミサイルは他の生徒、召喚物、遮蔽物によって遮られることがあります）
RaidSkill.DescEn: Launches a missile that targets the furthest enemy away and deals 750% damage on contact. The missile can be blocked by other students, summons or cover.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
ワカモのスキルで攻撃された対象はワカモの刻印状態になる。
ワカモの刻印が5枚貯まると、該当の対象は最大HPの1000%分のダメージが適用されます。
RaidSkill.DescEn:
Wakamo's EX skills will additionally inflict one stack of <s:SuddenDeath> to the target.
If the target accumulates 5 stacks, they will be dealt damage equal to 1000% of their maximum HP.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
60秒毎に、以下の効果を自身にすべて適用（計3段階）
攻撃力：30%/60%/90%増加
会心値：35%/70%/105%増加
被ダメージ量：10%/20%/50%増加
ATG回復速度：15%/30%/80%増加
RaidSkill.DescEn: Every 60s, gains one level of the following effect (max. level 3). Increases by 30%/60%/90%, by 35%/70%/105% and ATG recovery speed by 15%/30%/80%, but increases by 10%/20%/50% at level 1/2/3.

WorldRaid.NameJp: ワカモ（ホバークラフト）

RaidSkill.DescJp: 最大で敵8人に対して、順番にそれぞれ攻撃力の70%分のダメージ
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 70% damage to up to 8 enemies.

RaidSkill.DescJp: 最大で敵2人に対して、順番にそれぞれ攻撃力の250%分のダメージ
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 250% damage to up to 2 enemies.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
ATGの値がMAXの場合、リゾートを破壊するためにミサイル暴走モードに突入
リゾートが破壊されると敗北します。
ミサイル暴走モード中、ホバークラフトは不死身状態になります。
ミサイル暴走モードが終了すると、ホバークラフトに故障が発生し、グロッキー状態になります。
グロッキー状態の間、被ダメージ量が200%増加/会心抵抗値が100%減少
RaidSkill.DescEn:
When ATG is full, the hovercraft enters missile mode and begins targeting the resort. During missile mode, the hovercraft is <s:Immortal>.
After missile mode ends, fills the hovercraft's groggy gauge to the maximum. While the hovercraft is groggy, increases <d:DamagedRatio> by 200% and decreases <d:CriticalChanceResistPoint> by 100%. If the resort is destroyed, the battle is immediately lost.

RaidSkill.DescJp:

このミサイルを破壊すると、敵のストライカー、スペシャル生徒全体に対して攻撃力が400増加
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 450% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, increases all students' by 400.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
円形範囲内の敵に対して、攻撃力の450%分のダメージ
このミサイルを破壊すると円形範囲内のミサイル全体に対して、999999のダメージ
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 450% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, deals 999,999 to all other missiles in a circular area.

RaidSkill.DescJp:
円形範囲内の敵に対して、攻撃力の1000%分のダメージ
このミサイルを破壊すると円形範囲内のミサイル全体に対して、攻撃力の400%分のダメージ
RaidSkill.DescEn: Deals 1000% damage to enemies in a circular area. If this missile is destroyed, deals 400% damage to all other missiles in a circular area.
